'''氢氧化铟'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为In(OH)<sub>3</sub>，它最主要的用途是制备[[氧化铟|氧化铟]](III)。<ref>The Group 13 Metals Aluminium, Gallium, Indium and Thallium: Chemical Patterns and Peculiarities, Simon Aldridge, Anthony J. Downs, wiley, 2011, ISBN 978-0-470-68191-6</ref>它在自然界中以稀有矿物[[羟铟石|羟铟石]]的形式存在。

==结构==
In(OH)<sub>3</sub>属[[立方晶系|立方晶系]]，空间群Im3，有扭曲的[[三氧化铼|ReO<sub>3</sub>]]结构。<ref>Hydrothermal Investigation of the systems In2O3-H2O-Na2O and In2O3-D2O-Na2O. The crystal structure of rhombohedral  In<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> and In(OH)<sub>3</sub>, A Norlund Christensen, N.C. Broch, Acta Chemica Scandinavica 21 (1967) 1046-056</ref><ref>Wells A.F. (1984) ''Structural Inorganic Chemistry'' 5th edition Oxford Science Publications ISBN 0-19-855370-6</ref>

==制备==
用含In<sup>3+</sup>的溶液，如[[硝酸铟|In(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>]]或[[氯化铟|InCl<sub>3</sub>]]，和氢氧化物反应，得到白色沉淀In(OH)<sub>3</sub>。<ref name="Sato2005">{{cite journal|last1=Sato|first1=T.|title=Preparation and thermal decomposition of indium hydroxide|journal=Journal of Thermal Analysis and Calorimetry|volume=82|issue=3|year=2005|pages=775–782|issn=1388-6150|doi=10.1007/s10973-005-0963-4}}</ref><ref name = "Wiberg&Holleman">Egon Wiberg, Arnold Frederick Holleman (2001) ''Inorganic Chemistry'', Elsevier ISBN 0123526515</ref>
